`0Help for the Quickscan Menu ------------------

<F> Qscan Forward  - Perform a Quick Scan of messages in forward order
                     from a specified message number.
<R> Qscan Reverse  - Perform a Quick Scan of messages in reverse order
                     from a specified message number.
<N> Qscan New      - Perform a Quick Scan of new messages from the last
                     message that you read.
<S> Qscan Search   - Perform a Quick Scan in the fields:  To Name, From
                     Name, or Subject.  You will be prompted for the
                     field of your choice.
<X> Exit           - Exits to the previous menu.

Press ENTER to continue....`4

